docs.title: Projects
docs.text:
While I have expanded my learning over multiple types of software productions, I have directed my efforts toward the completion and release of multiple game deveopment projects, mostly as part of online game jams or personal challenges I have imposed on myself as part of my learning process.

These games have been published and the progress on some of them has even been documented on my Twitter.
